data.description: Wonderful single story home w/wrap around porch. Laminate flooring throughout with updated  stainless appliances in the kitchen, and a wood burning fireplace in the great room.  No carpet in this home!  Lots of storage throughout the home.  Brand new roof just installed , and a new walk in shower in the master bath.  The privacy fenced backyard offers lots of play area for the kids and has an outside storage bldg.  No HOA in this neighborhood.
